OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778267470
OL,3,CO'Neill describes election results as
OL,4,C'seismic'
OL,6,FLocal elections in the UK are "on
OL,7,Ftrack to be a seismic change in
OL,8,Fpolitics", First Minister Michelle
OL,9,FO'Neill has said.
OL,11,FDeputy First Minister and DUP MLA Emma
OL,12,FLittle-Pengelly said promising early
OL,13,Fresults for nationalist parties in
OL,14,FScotland and Wales do not show a
OL,15,Fdesire for change "on the
OL,16,Fconstitutional question".
OL,26,@nD@_OUpD@IO]wD@SOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
