CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778267470
OL,3,CO'Neill describes election results as
OL,4,C'seismic'
OL,6,FTaoiseach Micheal Martin said "more
OL,7,Ffragmentation in politics" is
OL,8,Findicative of a Europe-wide political
OL,9,Ftrend, adding that local and general
OL,10,Felections are "two different beasts
OL,11,Fcompletely".
OL,13,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer said
OL,14,Fhe was hurting from "tough" results
OL,15,Fwhich saw Labour lose hundreds of
OL,16,Fcouncillors in local elections in
OL,17,FEngland.
OL,26,@nD@_OUoD@ZO]rD@OOUsD@KO]vD@UOUvD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
