OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778267470
OL,3,CO'Neill describes election results as
OL,4,C'seismic'
OL,6,FIn Scotland, SNP leader John Swinney
OL,7,Fhas said he is expecting his party to
OL,8,Fwin a record fifth consecutive term in
OL,9,Fpower in the Scottish Parliament.
OL,11,FIn Wales, Labour is expected to be
OL,12,Freduced from 29 to around 10 members
OL,13,Fin the Senedd, with a party
OL,14,Fspokesperson saying they are "deeply
OL,15,Fdisappointed" they will not lead the
OL,16,Fgovernment.
OL,26,@vD@^OUwD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778267470
OL,3,CO'Neill describes election results as
OL,4,C'seismic'
OL,6,FThe leaders of the Stormont Executive
OL,7,Fspoke alongside Micheal Martin, Deputy
OL,8,FPremier Simon Harris and Irish Foreign
OL,9,FMinister Helen McEntee after a meeting
OL,10,Fof the North South Ministerial Council
OL,11,F(NSMC) in Co Armagh.
OL,13,FAt the Sinn Fein Ard Fheis last month,
OL,14,FMs O'Neill said the prospect of three
OL,15,Fnationalist first ministers leading
OL,16,Fdevolved governments showed the union
OL,17,Fis "cracking at the seams".
OL,26,@yD@DOUyD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778267470
OL,3,CO'Neill describes election results as
OL,4,C'seismic'
OL,6,FShe told reporters in Armagh on Friday
OL,7,Fshe did not want to be "premature",
OL,8,Fand votes are still being counted, but
OL,9,F"the outcome looks to be on track to
OL,10,Fbe a seismic change in politics".
OL,12,F"I think it sends a very strong
OL,13,Fmessage that people are tired of the
OL,14,Fshackles of Westminster, both in
OL,15,FScotland and Wales, but I'll let the
OL,16,Fleaders of the parties that have
OL,17,Fentered into those races speak more
OL,18,Fabout that," she said.
OL,26,@oD@XOUoD@bO]qD@AOUrD@`O]tD@AOUzD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778267470
OL,3,CO'Neill describes election results as
OL,4,C'seismic'
OL,6,F"I will work, in good faith, with
OL,7,Fwhoever comes out the other side of
OL,8,Fthe elections and work with them and
OL,9,Fwhere we have common ground and I
OL,10,Fthink that the common ground that we
OL,11,Fcertainly have with, I certainly have,
OL,12,Fwith the SNP and Plaid (Cymru) is in
OL,13,Fthe area of national self-
OL,14,Fdetermination."
OL,16,FMs Little-Pengelly said early
OL,17,Findications show "people are
OL,18,Ffrustrated with those that are
OL,19,Fcurrently in power".
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@OO]yD@ROU{D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778267470
OL,3,CO'Neill describes election results as
OL,4,C'seismic'
OL,6,F"I do think that this is an indication
OL,7,Fof a desire for change, but I don't
OL,8,Fthink that that is on the
OL,9,Fconstitutional question.
OL,11,F"I think it's a sense of, parties have
OL,12,Fhad the opportunity to try to
OL,13,Fimplement and to deliver, and there's
OL,14,Fa frustration with that."
OL,16,FShe added: "I think this is about
OL,17,Ftrying to give some others the
OL,18,Fopportunity to come in and deliver for
OL,19,Fpeople on core public services.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@YO]xD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778267470
OL,3,CO'Neill describes election results as
OL,4,C'seismic'
OL,6,F"So I do think we have to take all of
OL,7,Fthese things in the context in which
OL,8,Fthis is happening."
OL,10,FThe Taoiseach said he was hesitant to
OL,11,Fcomment on "politics of another
OL,12,Fjurisdiction" but cautioned against
OL,13,F"extrapolating from a local election
OL,14,Fthe result of a subsequent general
OL,15,Felection, they are two different
OL,16,Fbeasts completely".
OL,18,F"I think there is increasing
OL,19,Ffragmentation across politics
OL,20,Feverywhere," Mr Martin said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@SO]sD@LOUtD@MO]uD@AOUxD@RO]zD@
OL,26,AAOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778267470
OL,3,CO'Neill describes election results as
OL,4,C'seismic'
OL,6,F"If you look across the European
OL,7,FUnion, its coalition governments, more
OL,8,For less in quite the majority of
OL,9,Fstates.
OL,11,F"We've a fragmented sort of scenario
OL,12,Fin the Republic, so you are witnessing
OL,13,Fmore and more fragmentation in
OL,14,Fpolitics and in electoral outcomes.
OL,16,F"It's just an observation of what's
OL,17,Fbeen happening across Europe."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOUyD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
