PN,44210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1778267470
OL,3,CO'Neill describes election results as
OL,4,C'seismic'
OL,6,FThe Tanaiste said he would not comment
OL,7,Fdirectly because Ireland has "worked
OL,8,Flong and hard enough to disentangle
OL,9,Fourselves from British elections".
OL,11,FHe added: "I am reminded of the time
OL,12,FPresident Clinton made the point that
OL,13,Fthe people have spoken in that it
OL,14,Fmight just take a bit of time to work
OL,15,Fout exactly what they've said."
